ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectAuditor General of Canada ** Access to Information **
PrecisOrder (1) Repealing Order in Council P.C. 2017-517 of May 12, 2017; and (2) Directing that the Auditor General of Canada be granted access to information that relates to his or her statutorily mandated responsibilities contained in the confidences of the Queen's Privy Council for Canada as defined in subsection 39(2) of the Canada Evidence Act.
